body_html:
Byte array of size 3 doesn't fit well into 4-byte-aligned vector registers, but maybe some efficient packing is still possible...

@yf225 It was something related to PyTorch thinking that MKL was required and failing to discover it (instead I had self-built OpenBLAS)
